{"tid":2048921,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞銀認為本港樓價已見底 全年跌5%","createTime":"2020-06-03T06:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T07:14:52.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"22f3541708efcff04dcbfce3b26ead2faf879076","tid":2048921,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"瑞銀認為本港樓價已見底 全年跌5%<br />\n2020-06-03 HKT 13:37<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀投資研究部香港及中國房地產研究主管林鎮鴻認為，香港樓市受疫情衝擊，但二手樓價只較年初跌2%，主要由於供應不足以及利率低企。<br />\n<br />\n林鎮鴻估計，香港住屋需求每年達6萬個單位，但根據政府的房屋規劃，一年只能提供約4萬個單位，不足以滿足需求。所以當疫情稍為緩和，新盤的去化率高。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，本港樓價或已見底，今年整體跌5%，但目前出現大規模負資產風險不高。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，疫情打擊本地零售，租戶傾向與業主簽訂短期租約，並避免以固定租金續租。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529945-20200603.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529945-20200603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=c11edbf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529945-20200603.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4a7d57be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529945-20200603.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"fc132f167b029b54a96a3ae3552d2ce5850df7d5","tid":2048921,"uid":144843,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:12:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e4950e1086a0171ce94c2ffc2267cc36189b2ff","tid":2048921,"uid":3179,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"瑞銀呢啲垃圾 二月先話過全年會跌30% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c16361eadf7b25c1687bcfa6dc11aedeb8c6485","tid":2048921,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:20:40.000Z",